QeBypCw_text","default":"<p>In Italy, Easter is one of the biggest celebrations of the year. We wanted to bring that tradition to our American customers. This is our way of saying Happy Easter - with a real gift, not a fake \"sale.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggE2a9V-meS_text","label":"ggE2a9V-meS_text","default":"<p>No. This is a one-time purchase. No hidden charges, no auto-renewals.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggBr_m71saN_text","label":"ggBr_m71saN_text","default":"<p>That's the whole point. For the price of one Night Cream, you get to try every product in our lineup. Zero risk with our 60-day money-back guarantee.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2xFSx-IzP_text","label":"gg2xFSx-IzP_text","default":"<p>Until the timer hits zero or we sell out - whichever comes first. We have limited Easter Basket inventory and once it's gone, it's gone.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzn9yZbmxc_text","label":"ggzn9yZbmxc_text","default":"<p>Yes. Free shipping. No minimum. No catch.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gglFYYGZwgb_text","label":"gglFYYGZwgb_text","default":"<p>60-day money-back guarantee. If you don't love the products, contact us for a full refund. No questions asked.</p>"}],
